name: A Date With Taylor Swift
description:
Did you miss going on a date with Taylor Swift?

Go on a date with Taylor Swift this Valentine's Day on Ren'Py.

Near the end of your date, Taylor Swift Lyrics AI writes an unlimited number of songs for you to remember this February 14.

It won't be too different from a real date with Taylor Swift.
